---
description: Testing standards for TypeScript and TSX in apps/web-app
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

When creating testing for apps and packages it should contain in a directory
called `tests`. This `tests` directory should stay at the same level as `src` 
directory. Directory `tests` should contain `setup.ts` file and any other
config files inside it. And test cases need a folder and a 
matching convention for that.
